CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1939, pg. 15, reads: "These Crack Swimmers Will Splash for 'Y' in Big Meet - When the A.M.A. swimming championships are held on June 23, the Center Avenue 'Y' will have two of the strongest teams in city entered. Here are the teams slated to swim for the 'Y.'  Left to right: Women's team - Dolores McCoy, Jean McCoy, Katherine Bolden and Genevieve Howard..."
TitMainTitle: Centre Avenue YMCA women's swimming team members Dolores McCoy (Taylor), Jean McCoy, Katherine Bolden, and Genevieve Howard, posed on diving board in Centre Avenue YMCA indoor swimming pool
